  <name>K3b</name>
  <summary>Disk Burning</summary>
  <description>
    <p>K3b is a full-featured, easy to use CD and DVD burner, copier, ripper and more.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Burn and Copy CDs and DVDs</li>
      <li>Rip and Create audio CDs</li>
      <li>Rip DVDs</li>
      <li>Create mixed CDs (audio + data)</li>
      <li>Create video CDs</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
